4. Write a XML file which will display the Book information which
includes the following: Title of the book, Author Name, ISBN number,
Publisher name, Edition, Price.
i. Write a Document Type Definition (DTD) to validate the above XML file.
ii. Write a XSD to validate the above XML file.
PROGRAM:
i) DTD VALIDATION
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE bookstore[
<!ELEMENT bookstore (book+)>
<!ELEMENT book (title,author,ISBN,publisher,edition,price)>
<!ELEMENT title (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT author (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT ISBN (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT publisher (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT edition (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT price (#PCDATA)>
]>
<!--b)bookstore.xml-->
<bookstore >
